kitchens.title: Extended Stay America - San Jose - Edenvale - North
kitchens.description: Relaxed extended-stay hotel offering low-key suites with kitchenettes, plus free breakfast & a gym.
kitchens.address: 6199 San Ignacio Ave, San Jose, CA 95119, United States
kitchens.hotelDescription:
In a residential and commercial area a mile from Route 101, this modest extended-stay hotel is 5 miles from Hellyer County Park and 10 miles from Raging Waters amusement park.
 The casual studio suites feature kitchenettes with stovetops, microwaves, fridges and coffeemakers, in addition to free Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs. Upgraded suites add pull-out sofas. Kids 17 and under stay at no cost with an adult.
 There's complimentary breakfast and parking. Other amenities include an exercise room and coin-operated laundry facilities.
